	subrange as a primitive means of limiting resource consumption.
	This should finally resolve oss-fuzz 12738
	"graphicsmagick/enhance_fuzzer: Out-of-memory in
	graphicsmagick_enhance_fuzzer". (Credit to OSS-Fuzz)

